      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Rumors that you’ve become a proper carpenter have made their way here to #m10001000#. Naturally, I wanted to see for myself if they were true. You seem to have built up quite a bit of skill and experience—shall we take a look at your work?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "You sound confident! Very well, then. Please defeat #r#o20#s#k near #m10003000# and craft #b#t3010002##k for me. I’ll be looking forward to it."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "It seems you haven’t quite reached that level yet. I’m afraid woodworking isn’t something you can take lightly."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Let’s see… this is truly well made! I’m honestly impressed that you’ve built up this level of skill. I’d say this is more than enough to be called a proper carpenter. I admire the dedication you’ve shown in honing your craft. All right… I suppose I should give you a special gift."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "This #t4130000# is a special item that can alter an equipment’s abilities when used during crafting. It’s quite delicate, so the results may sometimes be disappointing—but if handled carefully, it could produce something beyond your expectations."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If you’d like to test the limits of your woodworking skills, I highly recommend giving it a try. Please keep striving forward!"
        }
